类 StoreController

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.StoreController

  • public class StoreController
extends java.lang.Object
    Class controller.SettingController is the Controller Class of 'SettingPage.fxml'.

    provided by URL, ResourceBundle, FXCollections, ObservableList, ActionEvent, FXML, ComboBox, Image, ImageView, Main, SetUp.

    This is the controller class for page the game setting page. Actions are supervised and reacted in this class. combo boxes are initialized with observable array lists. the icon of pacman, the icon of ghosts, the color of obstacles, the color of background, the difficulty and the map layout could be customized by provided combo boxes and buttons.

    版本:
    1.03
    作者:
    Boon Giin Lee, Heng Yu, Chen Liao

    • 方法详细资料

      • buyLife

        void buyLife(javafx.event.ActionEvent event)
        Method buyLife is the response function for clicking on button extra life. Buy pacman an extra life permanently at a cost of $1000 if the button is on click.
        参数:
        event - event is a java action event for on click.

      • buySpeed

        void buySpeed(javafx.event.ActionEvent event)
        Method buySpeed is the response function for clicking on button speed up. Buy pacman a speed up upgrade permanently at a cost of $1000 if the button is on click.
        参数:
        event - event is a java action event for on click.

      • storeGoBack

        void storeGoBack(javafx.event.ActionEvent event)
        Method storeGoBack is the response function for clicking on button go back. Go back to the setting page if the button is on click.
        参数:
        event - event is a java action event for on click.

      • initialize

        void initialize()
        Method initialize is the initialization function for loading the store page. data of the player will be loaded when this function is called. Calculate for current money left, current pacman lives and current pacman speed. The function will be called when the FXML file is loaded.
